title: Erman Eltemur
text: Erman Eltemur (born May 11, 1993) is a <a href="Turkish%20people">Turkish</a> <a href="karateka%20%28martial%20arts%29">karateka</a> competing in the <a href="kumite">kumite</a> −75 kg division. Born in <a href="G%C3%B6lc%C3%BCk%2C%20Kocaeli">Gölcük</a>, <a href="Kocaeli%20province">Kocaeli province</a>, he resides in <a href="Istanbul">Istanbul</a>, where he is a member of <a href="%C4%B0stanbul%20B%C3%BCy%C3%BCk%C5%9Fehir%20Belediyesi%20S.K.">İstanbul Büyükşehir Belediyesi S.K.</a>.
